78.6	Recreation	Recreation	Recreation is an activity of leisure, leisure being discretionary time. The "need to do something for recreation" is an essential element of human biology and psychology. Recreational activities are often done for enjoyment, amusement, or pleasure and are considered to be "fun". The term recreation implies participation to be healthy refreshing mind and body.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2d/Two_surfers.jpg/220px-Two_surfers.jpg
